title: Hour 1: The War On Rats
description:
Commercial jingles, quarters from the 50 states, Top 5 NBA floppers, and Tito Francona becoming Cheato Francona as the fix was in for Yankees-Guardians. Then, we discuss rats and cockroaches completely taking over cities. Plus, Rudy, Jack Nicholson's ad lib, Big Ben's podcast, and Tom Brady finally experiencing normal football.
